Start nodemon
- nodemon src/app.js -e js,hbs

Add to git
- from root     git init
- add file  .gitignore
- add node_modules/  to .gitignore
- git add .
- git status   to see
- git commit -m "Init commit"

Upload changed files to git
- git status 
- git add .
- git commit -m "Changes to about page"
- git push          equivalent to git push orign master

Push to heroku
- git push heroku master      pushers latest commit to heroku
